  "instructions": [
    "In a saucepan, heat the Appleton Rum over medium heat.",
    "Add the tomato sauce, garlic, onion, red chili pepper, and fish sauce if using. Stir until well combined.",
    "Reduce the mixture for about 5 minutes or until it thickens slightly.",
    "Stir in the chopped Thai basil leaves and lemon juice. Cook for another minute.",
    "Season with salt to taste and serve over steamed rice.",
    "For a spicy kick, you can add extra red chili pepper."
